Hermes
输入指令进入hermes模型配置，选择custom endpoint，然后按图示配置
hermes model
image.png
OpenCode
打开opencode.json文件，根据需求模型修改配置，并覆盖粘贴保存
{
  "$schema": "https://opencode.ai/config.json",
  "provider": {
    "compshare": {
      "npm": "[PERSON_REDACTED]/openai-compatible",
      "name": "compshare",
      "options": {
        "baseURL": "https://cp.compshare.cn/v1",
        "apiKey": "your-api-key",
      },
      "models": {
        "glm-5.1": {
          "name": "glm-5.1",
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
